data.description: PRIME TIME LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Over a half acre lot in highly desirable McLean 22101 location in sought-after Fairfax County McLean High School Pyramid! Perfect lot to build your forever dream home! The home is within walking distance of The Potomac School and the local schools include McLean High (ranked #3 in Virginia), Longfellow Middle, and Franklin Sherman Elementary. Situated right off Route 123, you're minutes to DC, Tyson's Corner, Arlington, Georgetown, Bethesda, or anywhere else your work and life take you. RARE FIND in McLean, or anywhere so close to D.C., with convenient access to the GW Parkway, Reagan and Dulles International Airports, world-class shopping, fine dining, business centers, Metro Rail at McLean/Tysons Corner, Capital One Headquarters, Amazon Headquarters, and the many renowned academic institutions within the D.C. Metro Area! House sold AS-IS. No sign, no lockbox, no showings inside the house. Contact the listing agent for more information.
